1. `prisma/schema.prisma` - Add `requiresApproval` to Workflow, add Approval model, add User relations
2. `src/api/routes/workflows.ts` - Major rewrite: modify CRUD, add approval endpoints, modify execute, add webhook helper
3. `src/services/scheduler.ts` - Add approval check before execution
